Package: crssplot
Title: Create Standard CRSS Plots
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Alan",
           family = "Butler",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "rabutler@usbr.gov",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-8625-6386"))
Description: Code to assist in analyzing and plotting CRSS data. Includes two 
        pipelines: (1) user specified yaml creates a set of standard figures
        comparing one or more scenarios. (2) A suite of generic plotting 
        functions setup to create the main types of plots used in CRSS analyses.
